Malcolm TUDOR, etc., et al., Appellants, v. UNITED STATES of America et al., Appellees. No. 6090. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 3, 1930.

Before DIETRICH and WILBUR, Circuit' Judges, and KERRIGAN, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties.
